    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan and are acceptable at this model risk level. CFD hemolysis predictions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump are deemed sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted.",
